Beta
version Bomb/Defuse map created by me. First Bomb map I did. like the name says [Firzt]usan so here it is. Ts carrying the bomb must blow one of the two bomb targets, That CTs have to protect at all cost. This map was inspired in De_prodigy map by valve. I Hope you like to play it and please give Feedback. =) New version! De_Firztusan_beta2 Change Log: - Much more cover in the Bombsites - Added more Nodraw on none visible surfaces - A little diference in the overview - Added Player Clip where it was missing in the first version - Corrected some visible bugs although some are still there (wont make a big diference) - More details - More realistic efects Now more than ever I need to get Feedback so I know how to make the final version! New screenshots" New nav. file made by CHIZBONE =)
